headline.print_headline: Ambrose Returns to V8 Racing in Australia
headline.main: Ambrose Returns to V8 Racing in Australia

lead_paragraph: Marcos Ambrose will return to V8 Supercars racing for the first time in nearly a decade when he competes in the season-ending Sydney 500 on Sunday.
